Preheat oven to 250 degrees F. Line baking sheets with parchment paper. Beat egg whites, cream of tartar, and vanilla at high speed with an electric mixer until foamy. Add SPLENDA(R) Sugar Blend for Baking, 1 tablespoon at a time, beating until stiff peaks form and SPLENDA(R) Sugar Blend for Baking dissolves. Spoon heaping tablespoonfuls of mixture onto baking sheets. Bake 1 hour and 15 minutes; turn oven off. (If meringues begin to brown, reduce oven temperature to 225 degrees ). Let meringues stand in oven, with door closed and oven light on for 8 hours or overnight. Store in an airtight container.